cs.EM, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.PL, cs.LO

Reasoning: 
- cs.EM (Embedded Systems) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on embedded and real-time systems and proposes a verification framework for such systems.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper discusses the evaluation of system properties and proposes a framework for verification.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with modelling and verification of systems.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper uses SystemC, a system-level modelling language.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper discusses probabilistic model checking and statistical model checking, which are based on logical reasoning.
